Darkness Radio presents Supernatural News/ParaShare Witches vs the Taliban Edition

Dave & Tim return from Michigan ParaCon to discuss the wacky world of the paranormal news from around the world.Witches square off to take on the Taliban, Ghostly child appears at a park, Elon Musk turns on Tim and enters the fray creating an AI Robot after warning against such things and the dangers of "Terminators",the cast of The Conjuring weighs in on the supernatural, plus ghosts, aliens, ufos and more AND Tim shares a strange personal story that may prove his fears of being cursed.
